author: CNET
description: Insta360 just dropped their newest 360 camera, the Insta 360 X4 Air. It’s extremely lightweight at just 165 grams (the same as the iPhone Air) and features dual 1/1.8-inch sensors, user-replaceable lenses, and can shoot at 8k30fps. The standard bundle which includes the device alone starts at $400 and the starter bundle, which is what we have here, starts at $440. Unbox it with us. #360camera #Tech #insta360 #insta360x4air #unboxing #360cam #360degreecamera
title: Unboxing Insta360’s Newest 360 Camera: the $440 X4 Air
